snippet.title: Amber Marshall has a shocking update before Heartland Season 15 Episode 9!
snippet.description:
Hey Everyone. Welcome to Soap Trend. We hope that everybody is doing well. We have some exciting news to share with you all in today’s video. In this episode, we will be talking about one of our favorite TV series Heartland. Our favorite actress Amber Marshall has a special update to all of her fans. And we also have spoilers for the latest episode of Heartland season 15. So do watch this video till the end to know everything.

Our favorite, Amber Marshall is regularly updating the fans in her Instagram about what she has been doing lately. And now as Heartland season 15 is all underway, and it has already premiered its eight episodes, Amber Marshall is back yet again with a special update to all the Heartland fans which she calls, “A. Marshall Weather Report” and she posted it on Instagram. She started the video with, “Well, Hello. And here is your A. Marshall weather report. It is a snowy and very cold day here in Alberta. It’s about minus 15 at the moment and it's been snowing for the last few hours and we’ve got most of our cleanup done.” #AmberMarshall #NewUpdate #NewEpisode
